      </section>

      <section class="section" aria-labelledby="agents-heading">
        <div class="two-col" data-reveal>
          <div class="col-text">
            <p class="section-label">agents</p>
            <h2 id="agents-heading">Works with the agents you already run</h2>
            <p class="lede">
              Zedra connects to local agents on your machine, using your existing accounts,
              tools, and plans. Approval requests and completion updates can appear on your
              phone.
            </p>
            <p class="lede">
              Get completion alerts, usage, resumable sessions, and code mentions in chat. More
