            </ul>
            <p class="lede">
              Missing yours? <a
                href="https://github.com/tanlethanh/zedra/issues/new?title=Agent%20support%3A%20"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">Open an issue</a
              >.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-visual">
            <canvas
              id="agents-canvas"
              role="img"
              aria-label="Agents like Claude Code, Codex, and OpenCode floating alongside notification, usage, and history cards"
            >
              Claude Code, Codex, OpenCode, Pi, Hermes, with push notifications, usage, and
