        </p>
        <div class="arch-wrap" data-reveal>
          <canvas
            id="arch-canvas"
            role="img"
            aria-label="The Zedra app on your phone streams keystrokes and approvals to the zedra daemon on your desktop; terminal frames, files, and diffs stream back over a direct end-to-end encrypted tunnel. A relay forwards ciphertext only when the direct path is blocked."
          >
            Zedra app (the UI, on your phone) ⇄ direct encrypted tunnel (Zedra Protocol over QUIC)
